Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.07,0:01:26.71,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}Even though it's easy to say "I love you"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.71,0:01:29.93,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}when you stand in front of me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.28,0:01:36.07,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}my personality stands up and gets in my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.32,0:01:40.86,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}I can usually pull through with my assertiveness
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.86,0:01:44.41,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}that's just how I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.41,0:01:50.62,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}But no matter how hard I try, I can't break the wall that's between us.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.62,0:01:54.13,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}I want you to realise… my feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.13,0:01:57.75,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}So I always send a gaze
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.88,0:02:01.67,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}of "I really love you" your way
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.67,0:02:04.80,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}with all of my courage!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.37,0:02:08.95,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}My flimsy silky heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.95,0:02:12.27,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}After meeting you, I finally realised
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.49,0:02:17.87,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}that I'm really clumsy when it comes to love.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.36,0:02:23.14,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}The scars from love that I'd almost forgotten
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.14,0:02:26.70,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}have started to ache all of a sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.70,0:02:30.29,OP English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}{\be1}Someday, like how I normally would...
