Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.70,0:22:33.23,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}extended its roots
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.23,0:22:41.09,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}and put out a fruit that was still unripe.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.09,0:22:45.79,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}The fruit that I wish would turn orange soon
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.79,0:22:48.87,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}is bathed in your light.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.16,0:22:52.61,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}The ideals and dreams just swell{\fscx300}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.61,0:22:55.52,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\fnGill Sans Std ExtraBold Display\b1\c&HBDCACF&}H{\r}ey, feel it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.01,0:22:59.46,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}Today, I tried eating an orange
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.46,0:23:02.71,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}but it was so sour I cried.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.71,0:23:06.18,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}I couldn’t leave it behind like I have been
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.18,0:23:08.76,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}so I ate it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.76,0:23:14.88,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}I love it… I feel like crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.60,0:23:22.02,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}I love it… I love it.
