Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.51,0:00:01.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, no, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.93,0:00:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to, really!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.60,0:00:06.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People are eating, so don't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.57,0:00:10.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's better to see it with your own eyes than to hear about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.76,0:00:13.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, see for yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.92,0:00:16.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's great, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.66,0:00:19.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aisaka is finally back.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.98,0:00:22.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.85,0:00:24.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, why are you girls screaming?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.67,0:00:27.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of which, Valentine's is nearly here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.73,0:00:30.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I doubt these festive youngsters will listen to anything I say.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.21,0:00:31.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Valentine's...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.73,0:00:33.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I nearly forgot about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.64,0:00:37.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop pretending! Those lies won't work on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.17,0:00:37.14,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.14,0:00:40.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You plan to make out while I'm not paying attention, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.29,0:00:42.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doing such indecent things at school...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.33,0:00:48.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, it's really pointless to give or receive chocolate at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.94,0:00:51.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,School is a place to learn.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.28,0:00:53.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-We're being lectured by Haruta...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.60,0:00:56.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Am I wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.39,0:00:58.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, what's school for?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.04,0:01:00.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Health care and PE, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.76,0:01:02.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.62,0:01:06.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu-kun, Aisaka-san, please come to the interview room after school.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.85,0:02:42.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu-kun, you still can't turn in your career assessment?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.72,0:02:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Aisaka-san, you haven't even turned the one from first semester in...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.50,0:02:49.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, I'm still discussing it with my family.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.44,0:02:53.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your mother wants you to go to college, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.53,0:02:54.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yasuko has{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.69,0:02:58.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My mother has always been a hard worker,\Nbut sometimes she pushes herself too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.96,0:03:00.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to be a burden anymore,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.65,0:03:02.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I'm not planning on going to college.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.54,0:03:04.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is what I wish for.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.91,0:03:08.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So Aisaka-san, what's your reason for not turning it in?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.85,0:03:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I come from a rich family, so I won't ever need to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.86,0:03:14.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's also why I don't need to study.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.65,0:03:16.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, there's nothing I want to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.54,0:03:18.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, you two...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.72,0:03:20.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I don't go to college{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.51,0:03:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand. It's just that you'll be on your own for the rest of your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.14,0:03:28.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't just blame stuff on others.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.84,0:03:30.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one will take responsibility for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.64,0:03:33.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I want you two to carefully think it through.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.36,0:03:38.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu-kun, you haven't gone against your mother's intentions, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.23,0:03:42.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After you've finished filling it out, bring it to the staff room.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.73,0:03:47.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The rest of my life, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.00,0:03:49.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.68,0:03:54.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, that's the career assessment form{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.38,0:03:55.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.90,0:04:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.05,0:04:10.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's impossible for me to think about my future.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.47,0:04:13.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't even recognise myself right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.56,0:04:20.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've always, always denied my present self.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.59,0:04:22.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Why is this happening?"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.42,0:04:25.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"What should I do to avoid it?"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.08,0:04:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can I know what I want to do later when I don't even know what I want to do right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.03,0:04:35.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's one thing I want to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.17,0:04:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to fall in love normally!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.88,0:04:41.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.76,0:04:43.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You don't even have someone{\fscx300}-{\fscx100}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.94,0:04:45.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.21,0:04:46.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone I like?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.11,0:04:48.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't even know who it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.01,0:04:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to be born into a normal family, then raised as a normal good girl,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.50,0:04:54.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and then have a normal encounter with a guy, and become friends normally.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.92,0:04:58.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to fall in love normally like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.64,0:05:00.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you using past tense?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.36,0:05:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, it's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.00,0:05:03.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, the conditions are already wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.66,0:05:05.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not normal at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.79,0:05:07.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by "normal"?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.03,0:05:10.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's right, and what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.89,0:05:12.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's there to decide those things?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.42,0:05:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it, why are you suddenly lecturing me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.04,0:05:18.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.27,0:05:19.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't mean that...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.17,0:05:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.60,0:05:24.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about the career assessments?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.11,0:05:26.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going home, I don't give a damn about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.84,0:05:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.77,0:05:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.80,0:05:38.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you already...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.19,0:05:41.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't I already refuse?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.15,0:05:43.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've always been{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.11,0:05:46.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Kawashima, think about it one more{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.40,0:05:48.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have time to think about it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.67,0:05:51.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye, I'm going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.91,0:05:53.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Kawashima-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.07,0:05:55.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing standing there?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.17,0:05:56.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and chase her!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.83,0:05:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.54,0:06:12.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want to do to my shoe?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.62,0:06:13.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.43,0:06:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.50,0:06:15.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have a shoe fetish?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.47,0:06:16.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gross.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.53,0:06:19.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.04,0:06:23.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.44,0:06:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you trying to set a record for long throws at a time like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.33,0:06:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.36,0:06:31.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.76,0:06:33.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why were you called to the staff room?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.86,0:06:40.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said I wouldn't model the school uniform for a school information pamphlet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.08,0:06:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you refuse?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.60,0:06:43.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that your speciality?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.09,0:06:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just don't want to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.59,0:06:48.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't even know how much longer I'll be at this school.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.80,0:06:52.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me that your fight with Kushieda{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.01,0:06:56.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, a trivial person like Kushieda Minori couldn't have an influence on my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.51,0:06:58.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, why did you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.79,0:07:12.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest, I planned to leave after the first semester.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.33,0:07:15.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,News about the stalker thing has died down too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.20,0:07:17.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never heard you mention{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.14,0:07:20.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I decided I wanted to stay here a bit longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.99,0:07:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to be with you guys tomorrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.00,0:07:25.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or even the day after tomorrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.45,0:07:27.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.91,0:07:33.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I watched Taiga get hurt, and understood her pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.61,0:07:39.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that, since I understood her,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.14,0:07:43.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd save her if no one else did, or something like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.57,0:07:49.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I realise that everything would sort itself out if I left.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.77,0:07:52.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kawashima, you{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.14,0:07:55.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.62,0:07:59.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why now, of all{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.30,0:08:01.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga? I'm really bu{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.61,0:08:06.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about the shop?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.27,0:08:09.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My part-time job at the cake store too...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.61,0:08:13.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They even made a cute uniform for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.10,0:08:16.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I contacted both places.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.41,0:08:19.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just rest, and don't worry about anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.04,0:08:20.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.68,0:08:23.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Situation...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.64,0:08:26.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ya-chan is sleeping, shh...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.11,0:08:30.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuji, how's Ya-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.08,0:08:32.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, don't worry about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.30,0:08:37.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank god, seeing her faint from my window scared the heck out of{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.87,0:08:38.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuji?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.34,0:08:40.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.98,0:08:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to buy something for Yasuko to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.42,0:08:47.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Ryuuji! What about your coat?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.45,0:08:49.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuji?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.39,0:09:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You left your cell phone, wallet, and key! Your eco-bag too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.01,0:09:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get a grip on yourself, idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.85,0:09:13.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, put it on already!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.18,0:09:17.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You too. Why are you like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.90,0:09:21.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wear this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.45,0:09:24.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm all right! You wear it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.93,0:09:27.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuji?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.00,0:09:28.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.94,0:09:30.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.81,0:09:31.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.67,0:09:33.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go home, seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.43,0:09:35.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! You're acting all weird now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.51,0:09:36.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.72,0:09:38.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuj{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.71,0:09:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What were you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.01,0:09:46.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.61,0:09:50.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yasuko fainted because of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.75,0:09:52.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my fault...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.49,0:09:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all my fault...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.09,0:09:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.31,0:09:57.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She has anaemia! It's her body!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.38,0:09:59.52,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not your fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.38,0:09:59.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I wasn't so useless,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.52,0:10:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yasuko would have more faith and trust in me...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.18,0:10:08.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She would rely on me more, and then things like this would never happen...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.67,0:10:11.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuji!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.18,0:10:19.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuji...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.45,0:10:28.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.65,0:10:29.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{w}It's all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.06,0:10:35.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's... all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.12,0:10:39.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.79,0:10:45.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right, I'm a super mum!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.60,0:10:58.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuji...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.93,0:11:00.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.27,0:11:01.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.84,0:11:03.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.70,0:11:06.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have somewhere to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.76,0:11:10.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's troublesome...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.59,0:11:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow and the day after tomorrow are\Nthe busiest times because of Valentine's Day.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.40,0:11:16.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, she really can't come.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.85,0:11:20.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think I'll be able to find a substitute at this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.34,0:11:22.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.10,0:11:27.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.53,0:11:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.70,0:11:31.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm saved!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.63,0:11:31.19,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.19,0:11:33.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.42,0:11:36.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to do something for Ya-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.63,0:11:41.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll help too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.10,0:11:47.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was fired from my part-time job at the cake shop?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.04,0:11:48.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.47,0:11:50.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's only natural.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.94,0:11:53.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure I'll be able to find another job.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.03,0:11:55.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Why are you comforting me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.65,0:12:04.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wel...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.38,0:12:06.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.47,0:12:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one's coming...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.00,0:12:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say it with a stronger voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.57,0:12:15.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, your face wasn't born for advertising food.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.58,0:12:17.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.11,0:12:19.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you guys are really working!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.96,0:12:21.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo, Taka-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.53,0:12:22.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.75,0:12:24.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haruta-kun, which one do you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.93,0:12:30.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They say if you buy big ones, bad things will happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.67,0:12:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.70,0:12:34.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I'll take that big one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.37,0:12:36.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May I have this one, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.05,0:12:38.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-That'll be 580 yen...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.23,0:12:40.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have an elder sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.55,0:12:44.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's not my sister, she's my girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.70,0:12:47.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye! Have fun with your jobs!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.27,0:12:49.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you feel cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.02,0:12:50.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go to a warm place.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.99,0:12:52.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.99,0:12:52.36,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.36,0:12:54.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world really has changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.05,0:12:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noto! Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.87,0:13:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I just happened to pass by...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.21,0:13:04.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, has anyone else come by?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.12,0:13:07.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For example, Ami-chan, or even Nanako-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.67,0:13:09.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kihara didn't come.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.12,0:13:10.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? No!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.07,0:13:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really care!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.53,0:13:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you see,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.40,0:13:16.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just wondering if Kihara will give Kitamura chocolate, or something...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.59,0:13:18.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what will happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.44,0:13:19.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine with it either way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.77,0:13:23.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, look Taiga, you care about "that," right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.27,0:13:24.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.19,0:13:25.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by "that"?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.48,0:13:29.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, why does Kihara Maya buying\Nchocolate for Kitamura-kun concern you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.53,0:13:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.66,0:13:33.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You like Kihara Maya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.22,0:13:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So people who realise their feelings after fighting really do exist...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.91,0:13:39.32,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just interested!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.32,0:13:41.92,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.92,0:13:43.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's so strange, Taiga!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.49,0:13:45.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think it's strange at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.85,0:13:47.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's perfectly normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.52,0:13:49.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A male's stamen and a female's pistil...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.72,0:13:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.69,0:13:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's something wrong with your brain!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.22,0:13:55.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.56,0:13:58.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.61,0:14:00.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be scolded if we mess around anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.69,0:14:05.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess there's no other choice than to summon the lethal weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.74,0:14:08.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you were by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.88,0:14:09.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.79,0:14:10.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.86,0:14:13.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, since you came...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.15,0:14:15.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, Stupid Chi', hold this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.62,0:14:16.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.45,0:14:18.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No thanks. Don't make me do weird things.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.74,0:14:21.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm beautiful, so I naturally grab people's attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.28,0:14:24.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes, you're beautiful! You're really attractive!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.75,0:14:30.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you should take this and say, "I love the chocolate here!" out loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.01,0:14:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.17,0:14:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want me to advertise?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.22,0:14:33.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.18,0:14:34.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.34,0:14:36.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would I do such a lame thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.05,0:14:37.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right, Stupid Chi'.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.62,0:14:39.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, how about you buy one for yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.93,0:14:42.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You could give it to Minorin to make up with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.75,0:14:43.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.69,0:14:46.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Contrary to popular belief, I care about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.52,0:14:49.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to get on good terms with Minorin, but it's not working out for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.42,0:14:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The shaking delicate heart of a Chihuahua{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.10,0:14:53.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, why are you making assump{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.13,0:14:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're embarrassed, I'll call Minorin for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.62,0:14:59.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My, Valentine's Day came just in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.81,0:15:01.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.18,0:15:02.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, isn't that Kawashima Ami-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.67,0:15:04.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right! She's so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.91,0:15:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her face is so slender!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.00,0:15:07.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's really Ami-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.58,0:15:09.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is she buying chocolate at that place?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.01,0:15:11.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ami-chan loves the chocolate here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.51,0:15:14.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even my model friends say it's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.30,0:15:17.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to buy the same kind as Ami-chan's!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.10,0:15:19.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, she can be helpful from time to time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.18,0:15:20.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.64,0:15:24.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I'll be right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.19,0:15:26.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuji, where are you{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.78,0:15:28.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, I would like this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.57,0:15:29.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C-Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.67,0:15:31.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kawashima!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.95,0:15:35.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really like chasing after people, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.66,0:15:38.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have potential to be a stalker.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.33,0:15:39.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.33,0:15:41.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You like running away, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.69,0:15:44.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not just from me, but from a lot of other things too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.50,0:15:52.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, I don't think it'd be better if you left.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.18,0:15:56.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, you'll disappoint everyone if you leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.10,0:15:58.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone adores you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.29,0:16:02.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.11,0:16:03.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.09,0:16:09.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.96,0:16:13.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, Taiga can't handle it by herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.89,0:16:15.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.56,0:16:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I'd be happy even if it wasn't everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.70,0:16:27.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get it myself either.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.41,0:16:31.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks! I'll be counting on you tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.95,0:16:37.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've reached our target already, so it's pointless to buy the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.22,0:16:39.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right, I'm going to give them out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.72,0:16:40.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give them out?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.52,0:16:43.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I caused a lot of trouble for people on the trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.26,0:16:48.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like Kitamura-kun, Minorin, and the Stupid Chi'.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.80,0:16:50.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And also...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.12,0:16:55.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I gave you chocolate, would you be happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.11,0:16:57.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.29,0:17:00.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What don't you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.44,0:17:05.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't be human if getting chocolate from you didn't make me happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.61,0:17:07.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.81,0:17:08.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I'll try my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.42,0:17:11.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just giving you guys store-bought chocolate is rude,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.31,0:17:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I'll try to do something nice with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.90,0:17:18.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hopefully I can make everyone happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.55,0:17:22.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it smells great!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.52,0:17:24.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to the shop already?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.67,0:17:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm all healthy now, so it'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.43,0:17:30.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to thank Taiga-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.83,0:17:45.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.47,0:17:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you bring us all here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.14,0:17:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today is Valentine's Day,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.00,0:17:56.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I made some chocolate to say thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.38,0:17:58.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You made it by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.23,0:17:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.86,0:18:01.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be such a waste to eat it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.76,0:18:04.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't that the chocolate you were selling yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.64,0:18:06.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're really good at telling lies{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.31,0:18:07.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.38,0:18:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The wrapping was nice so I reused it, but I made everything inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.40,0:18:13.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, this is for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.24,0:18:15.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.09,0:18:16.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't help you with stuff like that anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.95,0:18:18.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yesterday was an exception.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.58,0:18:19.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next is Minorin's.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.91,0:18:24.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know you went to save me during the field trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.27,0:18:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.40,0:18:27.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to be so formal...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.83,0:18:31.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll come to save you whenever you're in trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.64,0:18:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Minorin!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.53,0:18:34.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuuji.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.46,0:18:37.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You too, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.99,0:18:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Share it with Ya-chan, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.17,0:18:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.05,0:18:45.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next is Kitamura-kun's.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.73,0:18:48.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I put the most effort into this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.49,0:18:49.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, is that all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.52,0:18:54.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right, you were the person who carried me from the bottom of the cliff, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.54,0:18:59.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap, I didn't tell Kushieda to{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.70,0:19:02.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, gosh!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.64,0:19:04.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if my eyes were all white...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.63,0:19:07.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really didn't expect that to happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.69,0:19:10.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I rolled down like this, and there were some weird noises in my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.79,0:19:13.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I finally found out what fainting feels like.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.23,0:19:15.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like dreaming.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.05,0:19:19.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I felt like I blurted out things that I wasn't supposed to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.07,0:19:22.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I regained my consciousness, I started to panic...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.01,0:19:24.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think you blurted out?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.29,0:19:28.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really, really can't say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.39,0:19:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Minorin, I can't tell you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.60,0:19:30.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.88,0:19:33.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't! Anyway, it was just my delusion!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.41,0:19:34.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.19,0:19:36.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's something that no one should know!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.91,0:19:38.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be ruined if people find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.95,0:19:42.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't be able to live anymore because it's something really, really messed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.48,0:19:44.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.21,0:19:45.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't hear it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.87,0:19:48.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I heard nothing, right Takasu?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.26,0:19:51.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one heard anything, it's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.22,0:19:59.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.55,0:20:01.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think everything will be all right if you pretend you didn't hear it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.76,0:20:03.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What are you doing, Minorin?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.24,0:20:08.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga, you're glad that no one heard it\Nbecause that solves everything, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.46,0:20:11.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu-kun was the one who saved you, but he just didn't tell you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.52,0:20:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He didn't tell you because of what you said, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.48,0:20:16.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, Taiga?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.12,0:20:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't you just be honest for once?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.33,0:20:20.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.42,0:20:28.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kitamura-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.45,0:20:32.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My, you look scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.54,0:20:34.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid Chi'...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.01,0:20:34.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Takasu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.35,0:20:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think it'll be all right if you let Aisaka run away?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.63,0:20:40.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.97,0:20:44.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look here, Taiga!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.22,0:20:45.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.43,0:20:46.59,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.80,0:20:47.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you see me as?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.06,0:20:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Minorin, your best friend, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.59,0:20:49.98,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, no, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.98,0:20:51.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you say you like me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.64,0:20:52.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, believe in me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.73,0:20:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go of me! Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.10,0:20:55.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.74,0:20:57.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga, I believe in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.49,0:21:03.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think you're the kind of person to blame\Nothers for your inability to go after what you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.32,0:21:05.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or are you someone like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.23,0:21:07.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.84,0:21:10.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just want you to be happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.74,0:21:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just want the Minorin I love to be happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.17,0:21:14.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.58,0:21:17.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My happiness can only be....
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.13,0:21:20.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...can only be made with my own hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.57,0:21:24.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My happiness doesn't depend on anyone but me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.18,0:21:31.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is all we can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.64,0:21:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.31,0:21:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taiga!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.10,0:21:39.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amin, are you betraying us?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.07,0:21:42.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bad things will happen if you don't chase after her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.27,0:21:46.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu-kun, I'll chase after Taiga.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.06,0:21:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not done talking with her yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.30,0:21:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.51,0:21:52.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.60,0:21:55.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What will happen if I chase after her?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.26,0:22:00.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What will I do after I find out how Taiga feels?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.59,0:22:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She obviously wanted to hide it...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.51,0:22:06.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takasu-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.72,0:22:09.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.83,0:23:28.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Taiga, it's about to snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.26,0:23:30.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The laundry is still outside...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.89,0:23:32.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not just that,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.23,0:23:35.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I left a lot of things out.
